CHARLIZE CHUB raced off the rail, off the pace and failed to threaten. SOCIAL D chased three wide early, chased on the turn and faded. CHANGING THE KARMA was bumped and off slowly, then outrun. MAD MAXEY was off a bit slow, raced two wide off the pace and did not factor.
